data.description: Professional photos coming  Friday ! Welcome to your new haven in the highly sought-after Pennsbury School District! This delightful residence boasts a range of modern upgrades, ensuring comfort and convenience for the discerning homeowner.  Step inside to discover the heart of the home - an updated kitchen that combines style and functionality. With sleek countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and a bright sunny feel.  Experience peace of mind knowing that newer windows have been installed throughout the home, enhancing energy efficiency and providing a tranquil ambiance. Say goodbye to chilly winters with the tankless water heater for baseboards, ensuring a constant supply of hot water whenever you need it.    Escape to the outdoors and unwind in the great fenced backyard, offering privacy and space for outdoor activities. Whether you're gardening, hosting a barbecue, or simply enjoying the fresh air, this backyard oasis is yours to enjoy.   Conveniently park your vehicles under the carport, providing protection from the elements and added storage space.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to call this charming house your home. Schedule your showing today and experience the comfort and convenience this property has to offer.
